<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{lang}}">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">

	<title>포잉 홈</title>

	<meta name="description" content="">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="apple-touch-icon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="plugins/normalize/normalize.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="plugins/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="plugins/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
	<script src="plugins/modernizr/modernizr-2.8.3.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

<div class="po-container">
	<header id="main-home-bar">
		<div class="clicked-filter-layer"> </div>
		<div id="main-home-logo">
			poing.hb
		</div>
		<div id="main-home-menu">
			<ul>
				<li class="menu-sign-in">로그인</li>
				<li class="menu-sign-up">회원가입</li>
				<li class="menu-my" onmouseover="showMyList()" onmouseout="hideMyList()">
					<div class="my-box-size">
						<ul class="my-box" onmouseover="showMyList()">
							<li>예약</li>
							<li>티켓</li>
							<li>결제</li>
							<li>친구찾기</li>
							<li>설정</li>
							<li onclick="showSignOutBox()">로그아웃</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div id="sign-out-box">
			<div class="q-sign-out">
				<button>정말로 로그아웃 하실건가요?:( </button>
			</div>
			<div class="sel-sign-out">
				<button onclick="hideSignOutBox()">아니오</button>
				<button onclick="hideSignOutBox()" class="menu-sign-out">예</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>

	<div class="sign-in-up-box">
		<i class="fa fa-times"></i>
		<div class="sign-contents">
			<div class="s-title">poing.hb</div>
			DISCOVER, RESERVE, AND ENJOY


			<section class="section-sign-in">
				<div class="s-desc">최고의 레스토랑을 즐기는 특별한 방법.<br>검색부터 예약까지 한번에,포잉.</div>

				<section class="sec01-choice">
					<button class="s-facebook-in">
						<i class="fa fa-facebook"></i>
						페이스북으로 로그인하기
					</button>
					<button class="s-email-in">
						<i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
						이메일로 로그인하기
					</button>

					포잉 회원이 아니신가요? <a class="go-sign-up">회원가입</a>
				</section>

				<section class="sec02-email">
					<div class="write-in signin">
						이메일<br>
						<input id="member-email" class="input-email" type="text">
					</div>

					<div class="write-in signin">
						비밀번호<br>
						<input id="member-pw" class="input-password" type="password">
					</div>

					<button class="login-btn">로그인</button><br>

					비밀번호가 기억나지 않으세요? <a class="go-setup-pw" onclick="goSetupPw()">재설정하기</a><br>
					<a class="go-pre" onclick="goSignInChoice()"><i class="fa fa-angle-left"></i><i class="fa fa-angle-left"></i> 이전으로 </a><br>
				</section>

				<section class="sec03-setup-password">
					<div class="write-in">
						분실하신 계정의 이메일을 적어주세요<br>
						<input class="input-email" type="text">
					</div>

					<button class="btn-email-cfm">인증하기</button><br>

					<a class="go-pre" onclick="goSignInInput()"><i class="fa fa-angle-left"></i><i class="fa fa-angle-left"></i> 이전으로 </a><br>
				</section>
			</section>


			<section class="section-sign-up">
				<section class="sec01-choice signup">
					<div class="s-desc">지금 바로 포잉을 시작하세요!</div>

					<button class="s-facebook-in">
						<i class="fa fa-facebook"></i>
						페이스북으로 간편하게 가입하기
					</button>
					<button class="s-email-in">
						<i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
						이메일로 가입하기
					</button>

					이미 포잉 회원이신가요? <a class="go-sign-in">로그인</a>
				</section>

				<section class="sec02-email">
					<div class="s-desc">포잉에 오신 것을 환영합니다!<br>회원가입을 하기 위한 추가 정보를 입력해주세요!</div>

					<ul class="write-in">
						<li>
							이름<br>
							<input id="user-name" class="input-name" type="text">
						</li>
						<li>
							이메일<br>
							<input id="user-email" class="input-email" type="email">
							<button class="repetition-confirm">중복확인</button>
						</li>
					</ul>

					<ul class="write-in">
						<li>
							성별<br>
							<button class="choice-gender male">남자</button>
							<button class="choice-gender female">여자</button>
						</li>
						<li>
							비밀번호<br>
							<input id="user-pw" class="input-password" type="password">
						</li>
					</ul>
					<ul class="write-in">
						<li class="birth-date">
							생년월일<br>
							<input id="user-birth-y" class="input-year" type="text" maxlength="4">년
							<input id="user-birth-m" class="input-month" type="text" maxlength="2">월
							<input id="user-birth-d" class="input-day" type="text" maxlength="2">일
						</li>
						<li>
							비밀번호 확인<br>
							<input id="user-pw-cfm" class="input-password-cfm" type="password">
						</li>
					</ul>

					<ul class="write-in policy">
						회원가입과 동시에 <a class="go-policy">이용약관</a> / <a class="go-policy">개인정보 취급방침</a>에 동의하는 것으로 간주합니다.<br>
					</ul>

					<button class="sign-up-btn">회원가입</button><br>


					<a class="go-pre" onclick="goSignUpChoice()"><i class="fa fa-angle-left"></i><i class="fa fa-angle-left"></i> 이전으로 </a><br>
				</section>
			</section>

		</div>
	</div>



	<div id="main-top">
		<div class="layer-dark">
			<div id="main-top-body">
				<div id="main-text">
					<p class="main-text-1">환영합니다!</p>
					<p class="main-text-2">
					서울, 부산, 그리고 그 이상<br>
					포잉이 전국서비스를 시작합니다.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div id="main-search-box">
					<div id="main-search-form">
						<p id="main-search-region">검색할 지역을 선택해보세요!</p>
						<i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>
						<i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>

						<ul class="search-regions">
							<li class="sc-seoul" data-enable="true">서울</li>
							<li class="sc-busan" data-enable="true">부산</li>
							<li class="sc-inceon" data-enable="false">인천</li>
							<li class="sc-daegu" data-enable="false">대구</li>
							<li class="sc-daejeon" data-enable="false">대전</li>
							<li class="sc-gwangju" data-enable="false">광주</li>
							<li class="sc-jeju" data-enable="false">제주</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>


	<div id="po-contents">
		<section class="section-home">
			<div class="content-title">
				<p class="content-text-1">포잉과 떠나는 국내 미식 투어</p>
				<p class="content-text-2">미식의 시작, 포잉과 함께 하세요.</p>
